

Unit Testing
----------------

 .js-lang , we need unit-testing F.W

  --> to write test-cases
  --> to run   test-cases


  e.g


  --> jasmie
  --> mocha
  --> AVA
  --> nodeunit
  --> nunit
  --> qunit

  ...........

  mocha ==> popular and best unit-testing F.W




  ------------------------------

  Framework     :   mocha
  Assertion Lib :   expect,should,etc... with Chai
  Mock Lib      :   Sinon

  --------------------------------

  